text: Hoogelande is a small hamlet in the Dutch province of Zeeland. It is located in the municipality of Veere, about 4 km northwest of Middelburg. Hoogelande was a separate municipality until 1816, when it was annexed by Grijpskerke. ==References== Category:Populated places in Zeeland Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland Category:Veere
